title: Cherry Berry Christmas Cake
ingredients: ['250ml strong Jasmine flower tea', '50g dried cranberries', '50g Goji berries', '50g glace cherries', '50g raisins', '25g candied peel', '175g butter', '175g caster sugar', '3 eggs', '250g self-raising flour', 'zest of 1 lemon', '1 teaspoon mixed spice', '1 teaspoon rose water']
